This file documents the revision history for Perl application PhotoGame.

0.04  20012-04-24 23:30:00
        - photo_queue.pl generates md5, stashes them in the specimens table, and checks for dupe md5s
        - the uploader function implements the maxsubmissions properly, rather than relying on hiding the uploads form
        - photogame_queue.pl enforces max_submissions
        - Root.pm will try to create the queuepath, im not sure if there is a better place to put initialisation tasks
        - added a script to remove old photos in scripts/photogame_clear.sh
        - Added favicon
        - Changed some paths around
        - queue converts all images to jpegs and dies when debugging
        - tweaked register.yml to settle down debian

